'''仿纪录片'''（{{lang-en|mockumentary}}，「{{lang|en|mock}}」 与「{{lang|en|documentary}}」的[[混成詞|混成词]]）又称'''假纪录片'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=mockumentary|url=http://dictionary.sina.com.hk/p/word/mockumentary|accessdate=2014-03-22|work=字典|publisher=香港新浪网|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018203707/http://dictionary.sina.com.hk/p/word/mockumentary|dead-url=no}}</ref>或'''[[偽紀錄片|伪纪录片]]'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=伪纪录片|url=http://nrch.culture.tw/twpedia.aspx?id=21991|accessdate=2014-03-22|author=林木材|date=1999-01-31|work=台湾大百科全书 Encyclopedia of Taiwan|publisher=[[中华民国文化部|中华民国文化部]]|archive-date=2019-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191018013546/http://nrch.culture.tw/twpedia.aspx?id=21991|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是一[[藝術類型|种]]将虚构事件包装成[[纪录片|纪录片]]形式以作[[戏仿|戏仿]]放映的[[电影|电影]]或[[电视节目|电视节目]]。<ref name="Trompe">{{cite book|first1=Philippe|last1=Romanski|first2=Aïssatou|last2=Sy-Wonyu|title=Trompe (-)l'oeil: Imitation & Falsification|page=343|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=7pbJHd6i9nwC&pg=PA343|publisher=University of Le Havre Press|year=2002|isbn=2877753344|series=Publications de l'Université de Rouen|volume=324|access-date=2015-01-24|archive-date=2021-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203235042/https://books.google.com/books?id=7pbJHd6i9nwC&pg=PA343|dead-url=no}}</ref>这类影片常用虚构的背景故事来剖析或评价[[新闻|当时社会上发生的事]]，<ref name="Campbell">{{cite journal|title=The mocking mockumentary and the ethics of irony|author=|url=http://freireproject.org/files/Taboo2007BoratIssue.pdf#page=52|first1=Miranda|journal=Taboo: The Journal of Culture and Education|accessdate=26 July 2010|issue=1|year=2007|volume=11|pages=53–62|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726065500/http://freireproject.org/files/Taboo2007BoratIssue.pdf#page=52|archivedate=2011年7月26日|deadurl=yes|last1=Campbell}}</ref>甚有讽刺时弊的作用，有时甚至有嘲讽纪录片本身的作用，所以有人又将此类影片翻译为“讥录片”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=当代加拿大电影巡礼|url=http://mall.cnki.net/magazine/Article/DYSZ199804002.htm|accessdate=2015-01-24|author=李迅|work=电影新作|publisher=电影新作杂志编辑部|archive-date=2019-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191020013819/http://mall.cnki.net/magazine/Article/DYSZ199804002.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>影片可以是[[喜剧|喜剧]]或[[戏剧|戏剧]]的形式，虽然喜剧式的仿纪录片更为常见。

“伪纪录片”一词源于20世纪60年代。时至80年代中期，著名导演[[羅伯·雷納|羅伯·雷納]]在接受采访时将电影《[[搖滾萬萬歲_(電影)|搖滾萬萬歲]]》（''This Is Spinal Tap''）称为伪纪录片，这一词语因此开始流行起来。<ref name="Roscoe">{{Cite book|title=Faking it: Mock-documentary and the Subversion of Factuality|last=Roscoe|first=Jane|publisher=Manchester University Press|year=2001|isbn=0-7190-5641-1|author2=Craig Hight}}</ref><ref>{{Cite encyclopedia|title=mockumentary, ''n''.|year=2010|encyclopedia=Oxford Dictionary|publisher=Oxford University Press|url=http://oxforddictionaries.com/definition/american_english/mockumentary|accessdate=1 June 2013|archive-date=2016-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820204628/http://www.oxforddictionaries.com/definition/american_english/mockumentary|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Citation|title=Paul Shaffer on Letterman, March 20, 1984|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1lT-ONdy2ck|accessdate=2021-06-10|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2021-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610161230/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1lT-ONdy2ck|dead-url=no}}</ref>

